<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="safe-adj">safe <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /seɪf/    美 /seɪf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>安全的；平安的；无害的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Drivers should <strong>keep a safe distance</strong> from the car in front. 
司机应该与前车保持安全距离。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The missing children were found <strong>safe and sound</strong>. 
失踪的孩子都安然无恙。</p></div></div>